  <description type="morphology">Stems 4–9 × 4–10(–15) cm; tubercles 9–20 × 3–7 mm. Spines (8–)14–18(–27) per areole; radial spines (7–)13–17(–26) per areole, abaxial radial spines, needlelike, 6–11(–16) mm diam., stiff; central spines 0.15–0.35 mm diam. Flowers 1.8–2.3 × 1.8–1.9 cm. 2n = 22.</description>
